<cell id="cell-0"><cell_type>markdown</cell_type># Lab 3.10 — L3 Mastery Gate
End-to-end production RAG over SEC 10-K filings. Composes:
- 3.5 structural chunking (section-aware on `## ITEM X.` markers)
- 3.6 hybrid BM25+dense+RRF + bge/Cohere reranker
- 3.7 query transforms with cheap router (HyDE for vague, step-back for comparison)
- 3.8 ragas evaluate() — unchanged signature
The gate: faithfulness ≥ 0.85 AND context_precision ≥ 0.75 across two seeds.</cell id="cell-0">
